statements: SELECT * FROM Vehicle_Details;
SELECT make, model FROM Vehicle_Details;
SELECT year, make, model FROM Vehicle_Details;
SELECT * FROM Vehicle_Details WHERE year > 2015;
SELECT make, model FROM Vehicle_Details WHERE make = 'Toyota';
SELECT * FROM Vehicle_Details WHERE year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2020 ORDER BY make ASC, model DESC
SELECT make, model, year FROM Vehicle_Details WHERE make LIKE 'Toy%' ORDER BY year DESC
SELECT make, model, year FROM Vehicle_Details WHERE year < 2005 ORDER BY make ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT vin, make, year FROM Vehicle_Details WHERE make = 'Ford' OR make = 'Chevrolet' ORDER BY year ASC, make DESC
SELECT model, vin FROM Vehicle_Details WHERE year > 2015 AND model NOT LIKE '%SUV%' ORDER BY model DESC
SELECT * FROM vehicle_details;
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicle_details WHERE year > 2015;
SELECT model, make FROM vehicle_details WHERE make='Toyota';
SELECT * FROM inventory_management WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT location FROM inventory_management WHERE id = 100;
SELECT make, model, year, vin FROM vehicle_details WHERE year > 2015 ORDER BY make ASC, year DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT model, make, vin FROM vehicle_details WHERE make = 'Toyota' ORDER BY model ASC;
SELECT make, year, vin FROM vehicle_details WHERE year BETWEEN 2010 AND 2020 ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT * FROM inventory_management WHERE quantity > 0 ORDER BY location ASC, quantity DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT location, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM inventory_management GROUP BY location HAVING total_quantity > 50 ORDER BY total_quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_details;
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicle_details ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT id, make, model, vin FROM vehicle_details WHERE make = 'Toyota';
SELECT location, COUNT(*) AS total_vehicles FROM vehicle_location GROUP BY location;

SELECT vd.make, vl.location, vi.quantity FROM vehicle_details vd JOIN vehicle_inventory vi ON vd.id = vi.vehicle_id JOIN vehicle_location vl ON vd.id = vl.vehicle_id WHERE vi.quantity > 0 ORDER BY vd.make ASC, vi.quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_details WHERE year > 2010 ORDER BY make DESC;
SELECT make, model FROM vehicle_details WHERE make = 'Toyota';
SELECT id, make, year FROM vehicle_details WHERE make LIKE 'H%' AND year BETWEEN 2015 AND 2020;
SELECT v.make, v.model, i.quantity FROM vehicle_details v JOIN vehicle_inventory i ON v.id = i.vehicle_id;
SELECT l.location, d.make, d.model FROM vehicle_location l JOIN vehicle_details d ON l.vehicle_id = d.id WHERE l.location LIKE '%New York%';
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicles;
SELECT make, model, year, vin FROM vehicles ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT * FROM inventory WHERE price > 10000;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_manufacturers ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_history WHERE event_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicles WHERE make = 'Honda';
SELECT * FROM vehicles WHERE year > 2015 ORDER BY make ASC, model DESC;
SELECT v.make, v.model, i.quantity, i.price FROM vehicles v JOIN inventory i ON v.id = i.vehicle_id WHERE i.price < 20000;
SELECT vm.name, count(v.id) AS number_of_vehicles FROM vehicle_manufacturers vm JOIN vehicles v ON vm.id = v.id GROUP BY vm.name;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_history WHERE event_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM vehicles;
SELECT make, year FROM vehicles ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT id, model, year FROM vehicles WHERE make = 'Toyota';
SELECT * FROM vehicle_inventory WHERE price > 50000 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, location FROM vehicle_location WHERE location LIKE '%New York%';
SELECT * FROM vehicles WHERE year > 2015 ORDER BY make ASC;
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicles WHERE make LIKE 'Toy%' ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT v.make, v.model, v.year, i.quantity FROM vehicles v INNER JOIN vehicle_inventory i ON v.id = i.vehicle_id WHERE i.price > 20000;
SELECT v.make, v.model, l.location FROM vehicles v INNER JOIN vehicle_location l ON v.id = l.vehicle_id WHERE l.location = 'New York';

SELECT o.owner_name, o.phone_number, v.make, v.model, h.service_date FROM vehicle_owner o INNER JOIN vehicles v ON o.vehicle_id = v.id INNER JOIN vehicle_service_history h ON v.id = h.vehicle_id WHERE h.service_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01';
